Package net.adamcin.recap.impl

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RecapSessionInterrupter
    Internal interface that exposes an interrupt method for a RecapSession to check in case a long running sync needs to be ended for service deactivation or reconfiguration
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RecapAdapterFactory  
    RecapAddressImpl
    Standard bean implementation of RecapAddress for use within the impl namespace
    RecapImpl
    Recap service implementation, responsible for creating remote Sessions and constructing RecapSessions.
    RecapOptionsImpl
    Standard bean implementation of the RecapOptions interface for use within the impl namespace
    RecapSessionImpl
    Implementation of RecapSession using a BatchSession to manage auto-saves
